# BuildKit per-Dockerfile ignore.
#
# **/.env is load-bearing, not hygiene: ask.py and eval/run_eval.py call
# load_dotenv(REPO_ROOT/.env, override=True), so a baked-in .env would override
# the container's injected DATABASE_URL with localhost — and bake the OpenAI key
# into the image.
**/.venv
**/.git
**/__pycache__
**/.env
**/*.md
